{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2017-rnWebview/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Mark Zhang Blog","author":"Mark Zhang"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"858752ac-cf88-5f1f-af91-871716bbc932","excerpt":"React Native Version:0.51 RN 在 0.37 版本中加入了功能，所以想要在使用,版本必须>=0.37，发送的 message 只能是字符串，所以需要将其他格式的数据转换成字符串，在接收到后再转换回去，其实直接用和就可以 加载 html 属性用于指定加载的 html…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>React Native Version:0.51</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>RN 在 0.37 版本中加入了<code class=\"language-text\">WebView</code>功能，所以想要在使用<code class=\"language-text\">WebView</code>,版本必须>=0.37，发送的 message 只能是字符串，所以需要将其他格式的数据转换成字符串，在接收到后再转换回去，其实直接用<code class=\"language-text\">JSON.stringify</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">JSON.parse</code>就可以</p>\n<!--more-->\n<h2>加载 html</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">source</code>属性用于指定加载的 html，可以加载在线的页面，也可以加载本地的页面，代码如下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 加载线上页面</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Webview\n\tsource<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>uri<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'http://www.mi.com'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 加载本地html文件</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>WebView\n\tsource<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'../src/html/index.html'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h4>注意 ⚠️</h4>\n<p>在 RN 中可以加载 WebView，但是<strong>无法调试，也不能使用 alert 来验证代码 js 代码是否运行成功</strong>，只能通过往 html 写入东西（innerHTML）来验证 js 是否运行成功</p>\n<h2>WebView 与 html 的通信</h2>\n<h4>webview 发送信息到 html</h4>\n<p>WebView 给 html 发送信息需要使用<code class=\"language-text\">postMessage</code>，而 html 接收 RN 发过来的信息需要监听<code class=\"language-text\">message</code>事件，代码如下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// RN</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">WebViewExample</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Component</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">onLoadEnd</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>refs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>webview<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>postMessage <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'this is RN msg'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>WebView\n        ref<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"webview\"</span>\n        source<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'../html/index.html'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        onLoadEnd<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onLoadEnd<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> WebViewExample\n<span class=\"token comment\">// web</span>\nwindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> message <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>这里需要注意一点</strong></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">postMessage</code>需要在 webview 加载完成之后再去 post，如果放在<code class=\"language-text\">commponentWillMount</code>里由于页面没有加载完成就 post 信息，会导致 html 端无法监听到 message 事件。</p>\n<h4>html 发送信息到 webview</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// RN</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">WebViewExample</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Component</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">handleMessage</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> message <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nativeEvent<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>WebView\n        ref<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"webview\"</span>\n        source<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'../html/index.html'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        onMessage<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">handleMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> WebViewExample\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// web</span>\nwindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">postMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'this is html msg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>debug</h2>\n<p>RN 中 debug webview 和安卓开发中看起来是差不多的，连接好设备后，在 chrome 中输入</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">chrome://inspect</code></pre></div>\n<p>就可以看到安卓设备上正在运行的 webview 了，点击<strong>inspect</strong>就会开启一个调试页面，就可以进行 debug 了，RN 似乎默认开启了 debug 调试，直接就可以看到 webview 中输出的信息。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/home/static/04485499f7a5acf74b2b510cecacbfaa/4ac4c/webview_debug.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 42.567567567567565%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"webview_debug\"\n        title=\"webview_debug\"\n        src=\"/blog/home/static/04485499f7a5acf74b2b510cecacbfaa/1c72d/webview_debug.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/home/static/04485499f7a5acf74b2b510cecacbfaa/a80bd/webview_debug.jpg 148w,\n/blog/home/static/04485499f7a5acf74b2b510cecacbfaa/1c91a/webview_debug.jpg 295w,\n/blog/home/static/04485499f7a5acf74b2b510cecacbfaa/1c72d/webview_debug.jpg 590w,\n/blog/home/static/04485499f7a5acf74b2b510cecacbfaa/a8a14/webview_debug.jpg 885w,\n/blog/home/static/04485499f7a5acf74b2b510cecacbfaa/fbd2c/webview_debug.jpg 1180w,\n/blog/home/static/04485499f7a5acf74b2b510cecacbfaa/4ac4c/webview_debug.jpg 1243w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>但是我发现我打开的调试界面是一个错乱的界面，不知道为什么，无奈—！</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/home/static/4564e539e951e9430a2989dd65e4c007/84fcd/debug.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 14.18918918918919%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"debug\"\n        title=\"debug\"\n        src=\"/blog/home/static/4564e539e951e9430a2989dd65e4c007/1c72d/debug.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/home/static/4564e539e951e9430a2989dd65e4c007/a80bd/debug.jpg 148w,\n/blog/home/static/4564e539e951e9430a2989dd65e4c007/1c91a/debug.jpg 295w,\n/blog/home/static/4564e539e951e9430a2989dd65e4c007/1c72d/debug.jpg 590w,\n/blog/home/static/4564e539e951e9430a2989dd65e4c007/a8a14/debug.jpg 885w,\n/blog/home/static/4564e539e951e9430a2989dd65e4c007/fbd2c/debug.jpg 1180w,\n/blog/home/static/4564e539e951e9430a2989dd65e4c007/84fcd/debug.jpg 2011w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>注意 ⚠️</h3>\n<p>这里需要注意一点的，由于安卓版本的差异，所以内部的 webview 对 js 的支持程度也不同，<strong>为了保证兼容性，如果使用了 ES6，请转成 ES5，否则会报错</strong></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"RN Webview与Web的通信与调试","date":"December 20, 2017"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2017-rnWebview/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2017-jsDecode/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"JS转换转义字符"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2017-2018NewYear/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"再见2017，你好2018"}}}}}